      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable workhorse that isn't afraid of a little character? This vehicle has seen some adventures and shows significant wear, making it the perfect candidate for someone handy looking to bring a car back to its former glory! While it needs some TLC and mechanical attention, it offers a great foundation at an unbeatable price for those who see the potential in a diamond in the rough.",
